I'll go find a garage or something.

15
00:02:09,446 --> 00:02:13,417
See? That's smart.
Good thing I came along.

16
00:02:13,584 --> 00:02:15,257
Where you going?

17
00:02:15,753 --> 00:02:18,427
A little place north of Chartrand.

18
00:02:18,589 --> 00:02:21,035
