where I'm going?

37
00:03:25,889 --> 00:03:27,300
It's just right up there.

38
00:03:27,891 --> 00:03:29,632
And you can leave the plant.

39
00:03:31,028 --> 00:03:33,338
Well, no. I'm not doing that.

40
00:03:33,530 --> 00:03:35,305
