50
00:04:35,125 --> 00:04:40,131
<i>♪ But the risk of losing face
Makes the price much too high ♪</i>

51
00:04:40,297 --> 00:04:45,610
<i>♪ So I'll go on living the big lie ♪</i>

52
00:04:46,603 --> 00:04:48,139
<i>♪ The big lie ♪♪</i>

53
