82
00:06:59,036 --> 00:07:00,879
Back then, I mean.

83
00:07:02,005 --> 00:07:04,178
I didn't plan.

84
00:07:05,642 --> 00:07:08,350
I don't plan now, hardly.

85
00:07:08,979 --> 00:07:12,256
Well, things did not work out
the way I planned.

86
00:07:14,751 --> 00:07:16,492
