233
00:18:35,698 --> 00:18:37,541
Is it ever.

234
00:18:37,867 --> 00:18:41,246
- Do you read the newspapers?
- The horoscopes.

235
00:18:41,437 --> 00:18:43,383
Hold on to your hat, Shane.

236
00:18:43,706 --> 00:18:45,743
There was a woman.

237
00:18:46,676 --> 00:18:47,746
Where?

238
00:18:47,944 --> 00:18:50,254
She was watching the house.
She burned to death.

239
00:18:54,951 --> 00:18:56,589
She taught skiing.

240
00:18:56,753 --> 00:18:58,596
- You ever ski?
- What?

241
00:18:58,755 --> 00:19:00,598
- No.
- I tried it once.

242
00:19:00,757 --> 00:19:03,363
Couldn't walk across the snow
for the boards on my feet.

243
00:19:03,526 --> 00:19:06,507
But you told me, Ned.

244
00:19:06,663 --> 00:19:09,439
- You swore to me.
- Yeah, well, guess what.

245
00:19:09,599 --> 00:19:13,103
There are things in this world
that we don't know.

246
00:19:15,572 --> 00:19:17,882
Well... Hey, hey! Easy on the car.

247
00:19:18,041 --> 00:19:19,850
Fuck the fucking car.

248
00:19:20,009 --> 00:19:23,115
In this business... In any business,
but this business especially.

249
00:19:23,279 --> 00:19:25,782
