1076
01:16:06,012 --> 01:16:08,583
You're wasting your time, boys,
Pierre's out of town.

1077
01:16:08,748 --> 01:16:12,753
That's okay. We like big productions.

1078
01:16:14,988 --> 01:16:16,695
