It is?

1215
01:26:12,351 --> 01:26:14,058
Where's Pierre?

1216
01:26:14,920 --> 01:26:17,628
He's around here somewhere.

1217
01:26:23,729 --> 01:26:26,539
(PIERRE GRUNTING)

1218
01:26:43,148 --> 01:26:44,650
(STELLA SOBBING)

1219
