in one of their last conversations...

1220
01:27:12,978 --> 01:27:17,791
he expressed the opinion
that living is fun.

1221
01:27:18,484 --> 01:27:23,661
More specifically,
Pierre said that he found it fun...

1222
01:27:23,822 --> 01:27:27,167
when leaves move.

1223
01:27:27,626 --> 01:27:29,628
Perhaps what he meant
is that this planet...

1224
01:27:29,795 --> 01:27:31,775
and the lives that we have been given...

1225
01:27:31,930 --> 01:27:36,709
are opportunities
that we do not comprehend.

1226
01:27:36,869 --> 01:27:39,145
And so we misuse them...

1227
01:27:39,305 --> 01:27:42,218
day by day.

1228
01:27:44,576 --> 01:27:46,715
