and what do we see?

1230
01:27:49,348 --> 01:27:50,656
Nothing.

1231
01:27:51,083 --> 01:27:53,825
No leaves, no life...

1232
01:27:53,986 --> 01:27:56,592
for who knows how far.

1233
01:27:57,389 --> 01:28:00,131
And here we are...

1234
01:28:00,292 --> 01:28:01,737
now.

1235
01:28:02,361 --> 01:28:05,808
Are we doing the best
we can for each other?

1236
01:28:05,964 --> 01:28:08,103
For ourselves?

1237
01:28:08,701 --> 01:28:14,413
Or can we find it in us
to be more than we have been?

1238
01:28:17,910 --> 01:28:19,617
Carrie?

1239
